{
    "comment": [
        "Serialization registration for NitriteDB. NitriteDB persists documents into",
        "the H2 MVStore via java.io.ObjectOutputStream (org.h2.mvstore.type.ObjectDataType).",
        "GraalVM native-image requires every class in the serialized object graph to be",
        "registered for serialization, otherwise writes fail with",
        "'NitriteIOException: Error occurred while committing the database' and reads",
        "fail with 'MVStoreException: Could not deserialize ...'.",
        "This classic serialization-config.json is referenced explicitly from",
        "native-image.properties via -H:SerializationConfigurationResources because the",
        "unified reachability-metadata.json format is not auto-applied by Mandrel 25.",
        "The class list is the full object-graph closure captured with the native-image",
        "tracing agent while seeding and reading every CALM collection."
    ],
